---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import { professionalSystems,labSystems } from '../../data/observatory';
---
<Layout title="Systems — Shailesh Dudala" description="Professional and open-source intelligent systems across predictive ML, healthcare platforms, document intelligence, bounded agents, and execution harnesses." canonicalPath="/systems/">
  <section class="systems-index-hero"><div class="shell"><span>SYSTEMS / PROFESSIONAL + OPEN SOURCE</span><h1>The system around the model is the work.</h1><p>Predictive models, healthcare products, context engines, bounded agent loops, and proof-carrying harnesses—organized by the authority each one can safely hold.</p></div></section>
  <section class="v22-scene system-field-scene"><div class="shell scene-heading"><div><span>PROFESSIONAL FIELD</span><h2>Four consequential workflows.</h2></div><p>Sanitized architecture and synthetic traces keep the operating idea visible without exposing employer-confidential implementation.</p></div><div class="shell system-field">{professionalSystems.map((system,i)=><article class={`system-scan ${system.accent}`}><div class="scan-index"><span>{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span><i></i><small>{system.stage}</small></div><div class="scan-title"><h3>{system.title}</h3><a href={system.href}>Inspect system ↗</a></div><dl><div><dt>Problem</dt><dd>{system.problem}</dd></div><div><dt>Built</dt><dd>{system.built}</dd></div><div><dt>Changed</dt><dd>{system.changed}</dd></div><div><dt>Proof</dt><dd>{system.proof}</dd></div></dl></article>)}</div></section>
  <section class="v22-scene lab-field-scene"><div class="shell scene-heading"><div><span>OPEN-SOURCE FIELD</span><h2>Systems whose proof is public.</h2></div><p>Repository maturity and limits remain visible. Meta Harness and LLM Steering are the flagships.</p></div><div class="shell lab-rail">{labSystems.map((system,i)=><article class:list={{flagship:i<2}}><span>{system.stage} / {system.maturity}</span><h3>{system.title}</h3><dl><div><dt>Problem</dt><dd>{system.problem}</dd></div><div><dt>Built</dt><dd>{system.built}</dd></div><div><dt>Proof</dt><dd>{system.proof}</dd></div><div><dt>Limit</dt><dd>{system.limits}</dd></div></dl><a href={system.href}>Enter system ↗</a></article>)}</div></section>
</Layout>
